Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.19,0:00:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s go hiding in the wood.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.98,0:00:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Woah, woah, woah, woah! That’s the forbidden forest.\NAll sorts of creepy creatures live in there.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.85,0:00:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Look: it’s either here or shrieking shack. So let’s go!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.24,0:00:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I can’t believe it. We’re going from the scariest\Nplace in the world to the scariest place in the world.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.01,0:00:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. Let’s take cover behind this fallen tree here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.30,0:00:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright, Hermin?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.92,0:00:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I’m alright.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.90,0:00:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright, Ron?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.21,0:00:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be. -- After a Red Vine.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.52,0:00:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen – Hermio.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.51,0:00:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- What?\N- Why did you go in the shrieking shack if you...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.59,0:00:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...if you knew there’s a monster in there?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.62,0:00:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren’t you the one that’s always telling us not to –\Ngo out and do dangerous stuff and have any kind of…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.33,0:00:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- Fun?\N- Yeah!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.70,0:00:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.67,0:00:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I just thought that if for once I did something\Ncrazy then maybe you guys would like me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.16,0:01:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? Well, you thought wrong.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.92,0:01:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. No, no. Listen! Hermione...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.36,0:01:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You - you said my name right!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.79,0:01:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- Just now? Did I, Hermin-monster…\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.91,0:01:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That is close enough.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.65,0:01:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen: you don’t need to pretend to be\Nsomething you’re not just to get people to like you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.54,0:01:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-  I mean just look at me.\N- Yeah, but you’re Harry Potter!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.99,0:01:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah… yes. But maybe in the wizarding world that’s true.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.89,0:01:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the muggle world… I’m just a
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.10,0:01:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m something called a douchebag.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.55,0:01:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A what?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.79,0:01:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A douchebag, Hermin.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.69,0:01:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I play guitar when everybody is supposed to hang out.\NAnd – I make weird covers of Disney songs, who does that?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.86,0:01:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Muggles hate that shit. To them I’m just...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.08,0:02:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m just a douche bag. I’m like – I don’t know. I’m like...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.57,0:02:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Justin McCarthy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.12,0:02:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m like Justin McCarthy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.40,0:02:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m Justin McCarthy’s douche!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.35,0:02:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve got a confession to make too.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.14,0:02:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Back home – around my brothers.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.76,0:02:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m kind of a douchebag too.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.11,0:02:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Shia LaBeouf.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.78,0:02:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The prince douche.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.34,0:02:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But, hey. That’s okay. Because at Hogwarts\Nit’s cool to be who you are. It’s cool to be unique.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.50,0:02:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s alright. So hey: maybe you’re not very pretty...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.60,0:02:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...like Cho Chang. Maybe not as fun as Ron.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.02,0:02:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Or cool, like Snape.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.18,0:02:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what? You are smart.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.92,0:02:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Hermione.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.93,0:03:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And I for one would love to have a friend\Nwho could do my ancient runes essays.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.80,0:03:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- You mean it?\N- Yep, cause it’s due tomorrow.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.06,0:03:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Harry! Ron! Uh, come here!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.73,0:03:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh my good you’re so soft.\N- Thanks.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.57,0:03:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So you guys really like me!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.06,0:03:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, well just some things in life you can’t go through\Ntogether without becoming friends afterwards namely\None of them being taking on a 12 foot vampire.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.20,0:03:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- Argh!\N-Ahhhhh!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.54,0:03:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, We're dead as shit, we're dead!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.98,0:03:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I regret nothing!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.74,0:03:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in love with you both!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.25,0:03:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[neighing]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.94,0:03:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,None shall harm Harry Potter [???].
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.55,0:03:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Back! Back, you cowardly thing!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.49,0:03:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Run you creature of the night and know that\Nthese woods belong to the centaurs and their kin!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.06,0:04:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not worry, Harry Potter and co. The beast is gone!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.59,0:04:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.34,0:04:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Rise! Call me Firenze. It in the Centaur tongue means: friend.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.77,0:04:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. -- How did you...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.87,0:04:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Know to save you?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.02,0:04:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The leader of my tribe is a wise and powerful being.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.47,0:04:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He has seen the future and has charged\Nthe centaurs with your protection, Harry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.07,0:04:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,For you are destined for great things.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.75,0:04:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve heard that the centaurs were close to extinct.\NBut I never thought I’d get to see one in real live.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.62,0:04:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It is true.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.53,0:04:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We centaurs are a dying breed.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.46,0:04:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to a magical plague many moons ago,\Nall females of our kind have perished.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.48,0:05:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We have long searched for a human mate.\NBut none have ever survived.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.31,0:05:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Survived what? Www what survived?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.41,0:05:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Survived coitus, Harry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.87,0:05:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s coitus?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.23,0:05:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[whisper -- explaining]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.37,0:05:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, they died because of your giant horse gongs!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.97,0:05:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that’s... that’s funny.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.11,0:05:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it sounds like a funny problem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.06,0:05:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But it’s actually not.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.35,0:05:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. I’m... I’m so sorry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.72,0:05:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s alright.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.02,0:05:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen: -- we’ve got to get you kids back to Hogwarts castle.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.74,0:05:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Harry, unless the stars are mistaken you’ve got\Na Quidditch game that you must be well rested for.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.88,0:05:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow. Thanks Firenze, you’re so cool!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.87,0:05:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure am!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.36,0:06:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, get on my back!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.11,0:06:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,To Hogwarts!
